title: Recording Artists Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow Releases New Mixtape "MUDDY BROS"
text:
Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes announces the release of the new mixtape by Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow currently seeking blog placements and interviews.
Miami, FL (PRWEB) October 15, 2015
Today Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes announces the release of “MUDDY BROS”, the latest mixtape by Team Bigga Rankin Artists Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow. The mixtape is currently available for streaming and download at the Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes website .
The mixtape features 5 tracks, including those below:
1. Dj Winn - Intro
2. Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow - Muddy
3. Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow - Fanta Dreams
4. Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow - Traumatized
5. Antdeezy & Forgiato Blow - Stay
Anteezy & Forgiato Blow are currently seeking press opportunities, interviews, features, and more. They can be reached through the Team Bigga Rankin website .
For more info on Team Bigga Rankin artists visit http://www.twitter.com/coolrunningdjs
About Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes: Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes are the most widely distributed mixtapes in the world, with over 100 million downloads/plays generated by over 300 volumes officially hosted by major artists. Coast 2 Coast has a solid reach in the new music industry with a digital magazine, DJ coalition, industry tips blog, yearly convention, and more. Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes represents a unique opportunity for artists of all urban genres, from major to indie. For more information, visit http://www.coast2coastmixtapes.com .
